{
  "stem": "3277.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as soon we crossed the wires, all of a sudden, you know, Jude, Jude, Jude!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The German soldiers, Jude, which means Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jude!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jude!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And right away, they took us, and they started to make fun of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You lay down, you get up, you lay down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we were lucky that those were not the real Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were just plain soldiers, elderly people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they kept us, over the-- during daytime, in a little place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't give us-- what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's like in the country, where they keep the cows or the horse, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a place like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During the daytime, they took out everything from us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't give us any food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at night, they took us again to the border and said to cross it to the, to the Soviet side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they warned us, if they will catch us again, they will kill us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now, again, we were on the Soviet side and back, back to Bialystock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my brother used to make a little money because he was the watch maker.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a very terrible situation because we used to get news, what's going on on the Hitler side, the-- the-- the, you know, the killing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, whatever is in the books and the papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were in Bialystock for a short time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was about June, 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, you know, the Soviet soldiers used to look for those guys who registered that they want to go back, back to Warsaw-- to-- not to Warsaw, for the German side.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were hiding, but they caught us, and put us, right away, through the police station.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- also in a, in a little place where you keep like, bicycles, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
